{"tid":1479070,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有勇有謀嘅前線手足需要大家打氣","createTime":"2019-08-16T18:09:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T05:28:27.000Z","uid":198822,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f052c0786e651c6f88625c6eaf4703255731a808","tid":1479070,"uid":198822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T18:09:10.000Z","msg":"講真打咗咁耐，係人個心都會攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我相信前線嘅手足需要大量打氣，而唔係近日連登對前線嘅種種規則建議同埋批判<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n手法唔同，但係大家都係想光復香港<br />\n唔好因為手段嘅差異，而標籤佢地係無腦<br />\n唔好因爲唔熟悉前線，就將一啲標籤投射係佢地身上<br />\n無論如何，香港人一定要死攬呢班兄弟姊妹<br />\n<br />\n一人一句支持吓佢地啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n為香港賣命賣前途嘅人，一定可信過所有政客同領袖<br />\n你地比無數香港人更勇敢<br />\n有野要，香港人一定支援<br />\n我相信會有更多和理非加入前線，同勇武手足同行抗共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23db415aa671ca393fa044b92c15b707b365d0f4","tid":1479070,"uid":198822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T18:13:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a34bda99ec621ca9b01be495bbd7f5771037520","tid":1479070,"uid":198822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T18:19:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20d96bb2d5898f45f2eff0ff1830320ec6e38799","tid":1479070,"uid":101057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T18:21:02.000Z","msg":"核彈都唔割呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97304d09cc55b453f76fb93ca024bfde4c5d739a","tid":1479070,"uid":69914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T02:13:19.000Z","msg":"add oil"},{"pid":"2106f85fbd56b07c994fb00472d9213e31747733","tid":1479070,"uid